Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:10.05,Default-2,,0,0,0,,Černá loď!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.17,0:00:18.98,Default-2,,0,0,0,,To je neuvěřitelný.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.41,0:00:20.26,Default-2,,0,0,0,,Jsem...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:22.44,Default-2,,0,0,0,,Já jsem
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.47,0:00:24.81,sign top,,0,0,0,, Kanrin maru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.03,0:00:25.01,Default-2,,0,0,0,,na černé lodi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.03,0:00:27.05,Default-2,,0,0,0,,To je černá loď.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.65,0:00:28.67,Default-2,,0,0,0,,Jo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.00,0:00:30.81,Default-2,,0,0,0,,Je tak veliká.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.54,0:00:32.92,Default-2,,0,0,0,,A opravdu černá.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.04,0:00:36.28,Default-2,,0,0,0,,To je vysoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.74,0:00:38.69,Default-2,,0,0,0,,Japonci.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.08,0:00:40.50,Default-2,,0,0,0,,Japonci!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.70,0:00:42.28,Default-2,,0,0,0,,Johne!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.84,0:00:44.06,Default-2,,0,0,0,,Tak co?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.23,0:00:45.97,Default-2,,0,0,0,,Skvěle, pane Kacu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.43,0:00:47.09,Default-2,,0,0,0,,John?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.39,0:00:49.99,Default-2,,0,0,0,,Ano, to je ten slavný
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.03,0:00:51.67,Default-2,,0,0,0,,John Mandžiró.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.67,0:00:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ano, ano.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.90,0:00:53.65,Default-2,,0,0,0,,Cože?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.62,0:01:04.56,Default-2,,0,0,0,,Dělo!
